* Sun Jul 11 04:55:26 2004, pabs <pabs@pablotron.org>
  * raggle: added Raggle::Interfaces module, moved Ncurses interface
    related code to Raggle::Interfaces::Ncurses (Window, ListWindow, and
    TextWindow interfaces)
